In XML, a tag cannot contain another tag - so this is invalid code:

    &lt;img src=&quot;&lt;xsl:value-of select=&quot;product_image&quot;/&gt;&quot;&gt; &lt;/img&gt;

Use either:

	&lt;img&gt;
		&lt;xsl:attribute name=&quot;src&quot;&gt;
			&lt;xsl:value-of select=&quot;product_image&quot;/&gt;
		&lt;/xsl:attribute&gt;
	&lt;/img&gt;

or:

    &lt;img src=&quot;{product_image}&quot;/&gt;

To understand the 2nd syntax, read about [Attribute Value Templates][1].


  [1]: https://www.w3.org/TR/1999/REC-xslt-19991116#attribute-value-templates

